  <title><literal>Math()</literal></title>

  <indexterm significance="preferred">
    <primary>Dialplan-Applikationen</primary>

    <secondary><code>Math()</code></secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <simpara>Performs simple mathematical operations.</simpara>

  <synopsis>Math(<replaceable>output_variable</replaceable>,<replaceable>number1</replaceable><replaceable>&lt;operator</replaceable>&gt;<replaceable>number2</replaceable>)</synopsis>

  <important>
    <para><literal>Math()</literal> is removed as of Asterisk 1.4 and has been
    replaced by the <literal>MATH()</literal> (<xref
    linkend="functions-math" />) function.</para>
  </important>

